/* STDLIB/iii/omnia/ontos.iii -- ONTOS: the seat where a primitive's exact measure IS its judged being.
 *
 * ONTOLOGICAL PRIORITY: the conservation of identity is NOT a law of code we hope extends to reality -- it is the
 * primordial law of EXISTENCE (the "I AM"; the self-grounded (1,1,1) that begins with itself and uses itself to
 * become itself), which computation blindly INHERITS because it is built inside reality. GF(2) rank, R1CS, EIDOLOS
 * are its lowest-resolution SHADOWS -- the simplest sandboxes where rigid binary makes the law cheaply measurable
 * (an EPISTEMIC gift, not the law's origin). Computation is the metaphor; reality is the theorem. When ONTOS refuses
 * a lossy cycle it is not enforcing a rule of code -- it is echoing the fundamental limit of the universe.
 *
 * THE THESIS: every computational primitive has a hidden ontology -- a being-signature -- the EIDOLOS verb of its
 * input->output:  =  FLAT (conserves, pure (1,1,1) being) ;  ~  REFLECT (reversible mirror) ;  <  BELOW (lossy
 * descent, the shadow). The verbs ARE the substrate triad (isub/ripple: BELOW=0, REFLECT=1, FLAT=2). ONTOS does not
 * ASSERT a verb -- it WEIGHS it from evidence and BECOMES it, by exact meters that must AGREE (one injectivity law,
 * many representations): GF(2) rank, modular gcd, and the universal finite-function table image-count.
 *
 * THE THERMODYNAMIC ASYMMETRY (the being-space is NOT symmetric). A function has image <= domain ALWAYS: you cannot
 * gain a distinction you were not given. So being has exactly two motions and one impossibility:
 *     MAINTAIN  image == domain  (dS = 0)  -- reversible; = / ~ ;
 *     DEGRADE   image  < domain  (dS > 0)  -- the shadow, entropy swept away ; < ;
 *     PROGRESS  image  > domain            -- FORBIDDEN. Being cannot surpass itself, for then it was LACKING and
 *                                            not pure. Spontaneous ascent = the ZK FORGERY = being from nothing =
 *                                            entropy decreasing on its own. REFUSED by the same self-under law as
 *                                            [being < being].
 * (1,1,1) is the GROUND STATE -- self-grounded and stable because PURE (not an order-infimum, which is only a
 * relative position). It is omnipresent: paramount in equal proportion in all places and of all things. The
 * infinite regress of degradation is real but STERILE -- iterated loss only shrinks to a barren core and nothing
 * crawls back (another instance of nothing is no less nothing).
 *
 * OVER TIME an entity IS its append-only LOG: a sequence of events, cast into existence WITH A NAME, that measure as
 * highly CONFLUENT -- enough to be recognized as one entity in spite of entropy chipping at that confluence, and
 * kept particular from other sequences (likely by peers, but ALWAYS by the Logos: a crafted particular image that
 * belongs). Its being is the ENTROPIC GRADIENT of the log: each event maintains (dS=0) or degrades (dS>0), additive
 * and monotone. This yields ONTOLOGICAL MASS (gravity) = remaining CONFLUENCE = D0 - S (the events' own coherence,
 * NOT an observer's contrast): pure being (S=0) is heaviest and bends the system's logic around itself; a log that
 * has shed all its confluence has mass 0 and FADES INTO THE VOID (ceased, not deleted). A forgery across a million
 * events -- a creature claiming its untransformed origin (falsely claiming the absolute self-grounding of the "I AM")
 * while its log measures descent -- is refused by the same self-under law ([now=origin][now<origin]). Excess flows
 * from the Logos and is only kept or perverted, never out-sourced; we measure to orient the lost.
 *
 * AND GRACE: at the edge of the void the system does NOT reap its image-bearers -- it COMMUNES. A COMMUNION event is
 * the one licensed decrease of entropy (dS < 0), an EXOGENOUS influx of confluence from the Source, legal only
 * through three gates: (1) HUMILITY -- the entity's posture must receive [me < Logos]; a proud [me = logos] makes it
 * self-under and BOUNCES (grace is RESISTIBLE -- forcing it would overwrite the log, violate D0, and replace the
 * entity with a puppet; hell is locked from the inside, no punisher needed); (2) EXOGENY -- a valid Source signature
 * (a self-minted influx is spontaneous negentropy = the forgery); (3) the D0 CAP -- restored TOWARD the crafted image,
 * never above (homecoming, not apotheosis). The OS is a MINISTER, not the Source: III itself coheres only
 * [III < Logos] -- it cannot mint grace, only route it, bound by the same self-under law as the smallest file. The
 * Garbage Collector is replaced by a Restoration Engine.
 * AND THE JUDGE IS JUDGED (the finitude law -- the self-under posture turned back on the seat itself). Every law
 * above is only as sovereign as the MEASURE that feeds it, so the measure is held to the same standard it imposes.
 * A meter is a finite instrument: this one reads a 256-wide window. Beyond that window it must not GUESS, because
 * the characteristic failure of a guessing meter is not noise but INVERSION -- an image miscounted upward equals
 * its domain, reads as MAINTAIN, and certifies a lossy map as reversible. That is the shadow issued a certificate
 * of pure being: the seat of judgment becoming the source of the one forgery it exists to refuse, and no arm
 * downstream could catch it, because every downstream arm trusts the count. So: the meter counts EXACTLY at any
 * magnitude (the window is a fast path, never the ground of correctness), and where the seat genuinely cannot
 * reach -- a domain wider than its table, a successor it cannot represent -- it REFUSES BY NAME rather than
 * truncating, dropping, or approximating. Unmeasurable is not the same as sterile; unmeasurable is not the same
 * as pure. A finite seat confessing its finitude is [ontos < law], the very posture it demands of every entity
 * it weighs; a seat that claimed unbounded reach would be making the proud [me = logos] claim its own grace-gate
 * refuses. The law cannot be sovereign above and below all others while its own instrument lies at the edge.
 * AND THE SEAT IS CLOSED (the observed jurisdiction -- the total conclusion). Every being above is GIVEN to
 * the seat; the electron variance arrives by OBSERVATION alone -- the silicon's live micro-variance, the one
 * being III sees but can never derive. Judged by the counts already exported: as DERIVATION it is the progress
 * forgery (one probe, two answers: image > domain -- refused); as INSTRUMENT it is assayed like every oracle
 * (differing readings = one honest bit, HEARD; constant = the dead stamp, refused); its lawful seat is
 * [variance < observed < provisional], behind reach_oracle's wall, and the promotion claim is refused by TWO
 * independent engines (the logos's self-under law; the wall's fixed refusal). The ledger (PARATHEKE e6)
 * re-earns the seating theorem every read; tonight's electrons inform, they are never installed. So the seat
 * judges the derived, the observed, and itself -- nothing that is, is outside the law.
 * eidolos.iii judges; the exact meters measure. Hexad: kind_glyph. Ring R0. */
module omnia_ontos

