/* ptyxis -- THE FOLD, a real rank-carrying organ, brought here to BE JUDGED. The dependency runs this way on
 * purpose: ptyxis is PURE (it externs nothing), and that purity is its virtue; the seat of judgment is already
 * the heavy end of the tree, so the judge reaches for the subject rather than burdening the subject with the
 * judge. ONTOS never receives a generator or a matrix -- only two counts. */
